<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - LegalPracticeAI</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .not-found-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            padding: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        .not-found-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #dc3545;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="not-found-card">
        <div class="not-found-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-file-excel"></i>
        </div>
        <h2 class="mb-3">Form Not Found</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">
            The intake form you're looking for doesn't exist, has been deactivated, or the link may be incorrect.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted small">
            If you believe this is an error, please contact the law firm directly.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
